sentence.text: We aimed to investigate the effect of the AS to FEZF1 gene on non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) development.
The expression level of lncRNA FEZF-AS1 and FEZF1 was determined by the quantitative Real-time PCR in 160 cases of NSCLC tissues and their adjacent non-tumour tissues.

By GEPIA database analysis, we also found that the expression of lncRNA FEZF-AS1 and FEZF1 were significantly higher in tumour tissues than those of the adjacent non-cancerous tissues in 969 NSCLC patients (P AAAA 0.05), and lncRNA FEZF-AS1 was positively correlated with FEZF1 (r = 0.90, P AAAA 0.001).
